comments: Hartenstein (LAC) brings his hand towards O'Neale (UTA) and marginal contact occurs as Hartenstein sets the screen.
Gobert (UTA) is extending his arm into a vertical position and absorbs the oncoming contact from George (LAC) on his driving shot attempt.
O'Neale (UTA) makes incidental contact with George (LAC) as he is inbounding the ball.
Jackson (LAC) commits a take foul on Mitchell (UTA).
Covington (LAC) moves laterally into Mitchell's (UTA) path and makes marginal contact at the start of his drive.
Gobert (UTA) maintains his pivot foot as he receives the pass and begins his upward shooting motion.
Covington (LAC) is established in O'Neale's (UTA) path when marginal contact occurs during the screen attempt.
George (LAC) briefly places his hand on Mitchell's (UTA) opposite hip during his drive and marginal contact occurs as Mitchell loses control of the ball.
Gobert (UTA) is set in Covington's (LAC) path when marginal contact occurs during the screen attempt.
O'Neale (UTA) moves laterally into George's (LAC) path when contact occurs during his drive towards the rim.
Gobert (UTA) and Hartenstein (LAC) briefly engage and disengage during the rebound.
Kennard (LAC) maintains a legal guarding position during Clarkson's (UTA) drive towards the rim.
O'Neale (UTA) commits a personal take foul against Jackson (LAC).
George (LAC) moves along Mitchell's (UTA) path and dislodges the ball at the end of his drive, an ensuing contact is deemed incidental.
Gobert (UTA) briefly grabs Jackson (LAC) during the screen attempt.
As Mitchell (UTA) is inbounding the ball he calls a time out when the Jazz are out of timeouts, a technical foul is assessed.
Mitchell (UTA) commits a personal take foul against George (LAC).
